title: The Three-Eyed Bloodraven (video)
description:
A deep dive into the life of Brynden Rivers beginning from the point at which he took the Black. Was he a ranger? What did he and Maester Aemon talk about? Who is Coldhands? and more! Video available on Spotify. Published March 24, 2019.
